{"tid":452821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「通俄門」風波　馬納福特正式被起訴","createTime":"2017-10-30T14:44:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T04:01:45.000Z","uid":5303,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6fa4eef414c548207e7c42eb19d0e69198541fd6","tid":452821,"uid":5303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T14:44:23.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】在美國，捲入通俄門的總統特朗普前競選團隊主席馬納福特，正式被聯邦當局起訴。<br />\n<br />\n馬納福特被拍攝到在當地周一早上，離開位於弗吉尼亞州的寓所。<br />\n<br />\n早前有消息指，聯邦部門要求馬納福特和他的生意拍檔自首，馬納福特據報亦抵達聯邦調查局位於華盛頓的辦公室協助調查。而聯邦大陪審團決定落案控告兩人十二項罪名，包括洗黑錢罪名。<br />\n<br />\n馬納福特和前國家安全顧門弗林，被揭發在特朗普上台前私下與俄羅斯駐美大使，討論美國制裁俄羅斯問題。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=241386\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D241386&d=S6cB4ciL2boPXDS%2BKOaE2cPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=f9997d54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D241386&h=189618e4\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=241386</a>"},{"pid":"5a2e87a37501e42bf4c76025a61d0d489b369d51","tid":452821,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T15:12:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：<br />\n<br />\n三色貓、法國佬巫斯義、群龍共舞、優美開始、JR、RedBaron、Gladiclus、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><ins>證據一：五毛一見字眼空群而出</ins><br />\n<br />\n連狗對五毛問題視而不見、置若罔聞，與全連登作對<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451623\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451623</a><br />\n<br />\n【枕戈待旦】有關被連狗封鎖禁言之嚴正聲明<br />\